---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ShareButtons from '../../components/ShareButtons.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  currentPage="tools"
  title="2026 世足冠軍預測｜你猜哪隊奪冠？48 隊即時投票統計 — GAME8LA"
  description="2026 世界盃 48 隊史上最大規模！你猜誰是冠軍？投票後即時看全站預測統計。法國、阿根廷、西班牙還是黑馬？芭樂子帶你看各組分析。"
  ogImage="https://game8la.com/images/og-image.webp"
>

<div class="container">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="wc-hero">
    <h1>⚽ 2026 世足冠軍預測</h1>
    <p class="wc-slogan">48 隊史上最大規模世界盃，你猜誰笑到最後？</p>
    <p class="wc-desc">6/11 開踢！選出你心中的冠軍，看看大家都押誰。投完票即時看統計。</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Voting Section -->
  <div class="wc-voting-section" id="votingSection">
    <h2 class="wc-section-title">📋 選出你心中的冠軍</h2>
    <p class="wc-section-hint">點選任一隊伍，然後按下「確認投票」</p>
    <div class="wc-groups-grid" id="groupsGrid"></div>
    <div class="wc-vote-action" id="voteAction">
      <div class="wc-selected-display" id="selectedDisplay">尚未選擇隊伍</div>
      <button class="wc-vote-btn" id="voteBtn" disabled>確認投票</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Confirmation + Fate Card -->
  <div class="wc-confirmation" id="confirmation" style="display:none">
    <div class="wc-confirm-card">
      <p class="wc-confirm-text" id="confirmText"></p>
      <div class="wc-title-badge" id="titleBadge"></div>
      <p class="wc-comment" id="teamComment"></p>
    </div>
    <!-- Fate Card -->
    <div class="wc-fate-card" id="fateCard">
      <div class="wc-fate-header" id="fateHeader"></div>
      <div class="wc-fate-grid" id="fateGrid"></div>
    </div>
    <!-- 芭樂子擲筊 -->
    <div class="wc-jiao-section" id="jiaoSection">
      <button class="wc-jiao-btn" id="jiaoBtn" onclick="askGods()">🥠 讓芭樂子擲筊問問神明怎麼看</button>
      <div class="wc-jiao-result" id="jiaoResult" style="display:none"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="wc-confirm-actions">
      <button class="wc-revote-btn" onclick="revote()">🔄 改變心意？換一隊看看</button>
      <p class="wc-confirm-sub">👇 來看看大家都押誰</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Results Section -->
  <div class="wc-results-section" id="resultsSection" style="display:none">
    <h2 class="wc-section-title">📊 全站預測統計</h2>
    <p class="wc-total-votes" id="totalVotes"></p>
    <div class="wc-chart" id="chart"></div>
    <p class="wc-share-prompt">🔥 分享給朋友一起預測！看誰的眼光最準</p>
  </div>

  <!-- SEO Static Section -->
  <section class="wc-seo-section">
    <h2>2026 世界盃你該知道的事</h2>

    <h3>史上最大規模：48 隊、104 場比賽</h3>
    <p>2026 年 FIFA 世界盃是史上第一次 48 隊參賽的世界盃，也是第一次由三個國家聯合主辦——美國、加拿大、墨西哥。賽事從 6 月 11 日打到 7 月 19 日，總共 104 場比賽。分成 12 組（A 到 L），每組 4 隊，前兩名晉級 32 強淘汰賽。簡單說：場次多到你可以天天看球不睡覺。</p>

    <h3>死亡之組：I 組</h3>
    <p>法國（FIFA 排名第 1）、塞內加爾（第 18）、挪威（第 22）、伊拉克（第 61）。法國雖然排名第一但別以為穩了——塞內加爾在 2022 年就展現過非洲冠軍的實力，挪威有哈蘭德這個進球機器。芭樂子覺得這組每場都是硬仗，小組第二搞不好比其他組冠軍還強。</p>

    <h3>首次參賽的新面孔</h3>
    <p>維德角 🇨🇻、乘拉索 🇨🇼、約旦 🇯🇴、烏茲別克 🇺🇿 都是世界盃處女秀！特別是維德角，這個只有 50 萬人口的島國能踢進世界盃，根本是足球界的灰姑娘故事。</p>

    <h3>缺席的強隊</h3>
    <p>義大利連續第三屆缺席世界盃！上一次他們參賽是 2014 年巴西世界盃。四屆冠軍變成看台觀眾，芭樂子只能說：足球就是這麼殘酷，過去的榮耀不能當飯吃。</p>

    <h3>芭樂子的冠軍分析</h3>
    <p>說實話，法國跟阿根廷是兩大熱門，這誰都看得出來。但芭樂子要提醒你：2022 年之前誰猜到阿根廷能奪冠？2018 年之前誰猜到法國那批年輕人能封王？世界盃的魅力就在於「意外」。西班牙這兩年的年輕球員爆發力驚人，英格蘭的陣容深度也是頂級，巴西雖然近年起伏大但底蘊在那裡。至於黑馬？芭樂子看好日本——他們在 2022 年連贏德國和西班牙不是運氣，是實力。</p>

    <p>不管你選誰，記住一件事：世界盃四年才一次，享受比賽比猜對答案更重要。當然啦，如果你猜對了，截圖炫耀是基本禮貌 😏</p>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <div class="wc-cta-bar">
    <p>🎲 不知道選誰？讓命運來決定</p>
    <div class="wc-cta-links">
      <a href="/tools/bless-blocks/" class="wc-cta-link">🥢 擲筊問問神明</a>
      <a href="/tools/blackjack/" class="wc-cta-link">🃏 AI 21 點</a>
      <a href="/tools/" class="wc-cta-link">🔧 8LA 工具箱</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align:center;margin:2rem 0">
    <a href="/tools/" class="btn-outline">&larr; 回工具箱</a>
  </div>

  <ShareButtons title="2026 世足冠軍預測｜你猜哪隊奪冠？" heading="⚽ 世足開打在即，你押哪隊？" />
</div>

<!-- ===== SoftwareApplication Schema ===== -->
<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebApplication",
  "name": "2026 世足冠軍預測投票工具",
  "url": "https://game8la.com/tools/worldcup-2026/",
  "applicationCategory": "EntertainmentApplication",
  "operatingSystem": "Web",
  "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "price": "0", "priceCurrency": "TWD" },
  "description": "2026 世界盃 48 隊冠軍預測投票工具，即時統計全站投票結果，支援 12 組別瀏覽。"
})} />

<!-- ===== BreadcrumbList Schema ===== -->
<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "首頁", "item": "https://game8la.com/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "工具箱", "item": "https://game8la.com/tools/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "2026 世足冠軍預測", "item": "https://game8la.com/tools/worldcup-2026/" }
  ]
})} />

<!-- ===== FAQ Schema ===== -->
<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "2026 世界盃有幾隊參賽？",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "2026 年 FIFA 世界盃首次擴大為 48 隊參賽，分成 12 組（A 到 L），每組 4 隊。這是世界盃歷史上規模最大的一屆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "2026 世界盃在哪裡舉辦？",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "2026 世界盃由美國、加拿大和墨西哥三國聯合主辦，是史上第一次由三個國家共同舉辦世界盃。決賽將在美國紐約/紐澤西的大都會體育場舉行。"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "2026 世界盃什麼時候開始？",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "2026 世界盃於 6 月 11 日開幕，7 月 19 日決賽，為期約 39 天，總共進行 104 場比賽。"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "2026 世界盃冠軍熱門是誰？",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "根據 FIFA 排名和博彩賠率，法國（排名第 1）、阿根廷（排名第 3）、西班牙（排名第 2）、英格蘭（排名第 4）是主要的冠軍熱門。巴西和葡萄牙也被看好。"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "哪些隊伍是首次參加世界盃？",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "維德角、乘拉索（庫拉索）、約旦和烏茲別克都是首次參加世界盃決賽圈。其中維德角是人口最少的參賽國之一。"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "2026 世界盃的死亡之組是哪一組？",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "I 組被普遍認為是死亡之組，包含 FIFA 排名第 1 的法國、非洲強隊塞內加爾（第 18）、擁有哈蘭德的挪威（第 22）以及伊拉克（第 61）。"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "義大利有參加 2026 世界盃嗎？",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "沒有。義大利連續第三屆無緣世界盃（2018、2022、2026），這是四屆冠軍得主歷史上最長的缺席紀錄。"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "2026 世界盃賽制有什麼改變？",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "2026 世界盃從 32 隊擴大為 48 隊，分成 12 組。小組賽仍為每組 4 隊循環賽，前兩名加上 8 支最佳第三名晉級 32 強淘汰賽，之後為單淘汰賽制直到決賽。"
      }
    }
  ]
})} />

<style is:global>
  /* === HERO === */
  .wc-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .wc-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .wc-slogan {
    color: #f5b800;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .wc-desc {
    color: #bbb;
    font-size: 1rem;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* === SECTION TITLES === */
  .wc-section-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .wc-section-hint {
    text-align: center;
    color: #999;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* === VOTING SECTION === */
  .wc-voting-section {
    padding: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }

  /* === GROUPS GRID === */
  .wc-groups-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .wc-group-card {
    background: #1a1a2e;
    border: 1px solid #2a4a35;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .wc-group-card:hover {
    border-color: #3d7a50;
  }

  .wc-group-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f5b800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2a4a35;
  }

  .wc-team-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
  }
  .wc-team-item:hover {
    background: rgba(245, 184, 0, 0.08);
    border-color: rgba(245, 184, 0, 0.3);
  }
  .wc-team-item.wc-selected {
    background: rgba(245, 184, 0, 0.12);
    border-color: #f5b800;
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(245, 184, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .wc-team-flag {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .wc-team-name {
    flex: 1;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #eee;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .wc-team-rank {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #888;
    background: #222;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* === VOTE ACTION === */
  .wc-vote-action {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: #1a1a2e;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #2a4a35;
  }
  .wc-selected-display {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    min-height: 1.5em;
  }
  .wc-selected-display.wc-has-pick {
    color: #f5b800;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }
  .wc-vote-btn {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a472a, #2d6b3f);
    color: #f5b800;
    border: 2px solid #f5b800;
    padding: 0.8rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    opacity: 0.5;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .wc-vote-btn.wc-active {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }
  .wc-vote-btn.wc-active:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d6b3f, #3d8b55);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(245, 184, 0, 0.3);
  }

  /* === CONFIRMATION === */
  .wc-confirmation {
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .wc-confirm-card {
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a472a, #0d2818);
    border: 2px solid #f5b800;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(245, 184, 0, 0.15);
  }
  .wc-confirm-text {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f5b800;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .wc-confirm-sub {
    color: #bbb;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .wc-title-badge {
    margin: 0.8rem 0;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245,184,0,0.15), rgba(245,184,0,0.05));
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,184,0,0.4);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: #f5b800;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .wc-title-badge strong { color: #ffd700; }

  .wc-comment {
    color: #ccc;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0.8rem 0;
    padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border-left: 3px solid #f5b800;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  .wc-fate-card {
    margin: 1.2rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(26,71,42,0.4), rgba(13,40,24,0.6));
    border: 1px solid rgba(57,255,20,0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .wc-fate-header {
    padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(57,255,20,0.1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(57,255,20,0.15);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .wc-fate-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .wc-fate-item {
    padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .wc-fate-item:nth-child(odd) { border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
  .wc-fate-label { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.82rem; }
  .wc-fate-val { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .wc-fate-prob { color: #f5b800; font-size: 1.1rem; }

  .wc-jiao-section { margin: 1rem 0; text-align: center; }
  .wc-jiao-btn {
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245,184,0,0.15), rgba(245,184,0,0.08));
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,184,0,0.4);
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: #f5b800;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .wc-jiao-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(245,184,0,0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(245,184,0,0.2);
  }
  .wc-jiao-result { margin-top: 1rem; }
  .wc-jiao-throws { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .wc-jiao-icon { font-size: 1.2rem; padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
  .wc-jiao-holy { background: rgba(57,255,20,0.12); color: #39FF14; }
  .wc-jiao-laugh { background: rgba(245,184,0,0.1); color: #f5b800; }
  .wc-jiao-dark { background: rgba(255,50,50,0.1); color: #ff6b6b; }
  .wc-jiao-verdict {
    padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }
  .wc-jiao-yes { background: rgba(57,255,20,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(57,255,20,0.3); color: #39FF14; }
  .wc-jiao-maybe { background: rgba(245,184,0,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(245,184,0,0.25); color: #f5b800; }
  .wc-jiao-hmm { background: rgba(255,150,50,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,150,50,0.25); color: #ff9632; }
  .wc-jiao-no { background: rgba(255,50,50,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,50,50,0.25); color: #ff6b6b; }
  .wc-jiao-retry {
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .wc-jiao-retry:hover { border-color: #f5b800; color: #f5b800; }

  .wc-confirm-actions {
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .wc-revote-btn {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .wc-revote-btn:hover {
    border-color: #f5b800;
    color: #f5b800;
    background: rgba(245,184,0,0.08);
  }

  /* === RESULTS === */
  .wc-results-section {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }
  .wc-total-votes {
    text-align: center;
    color: #888;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .wc-chart {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .wc-chart-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }
  .wc-chart-label {
    min-width: 100px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #ddd;
    text-align: right;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }
  .wc-chart-bar-wrap {
    flex: 1;
    height: 28px;
